{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/menusignalname\/notify"]}],"metadata":{"title":"MenuSignalName.notify","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"roleHeading":"Case","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO14MenuSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuSignalName"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuSignalName\/notify","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}]}]}],"sections":[],"references":{"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names":{"titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"canonical parameter names"}],"type":"link","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","title":"canonical parameter names","url":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"}